  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> The Scribe may now alter a single documented event per week.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The Scribe records major events of the session.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> They may rewrite a single line of documentation each week (must be approved for fairness).</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If they rewrite a historical moment, it changes how that moment is remembered in class discussions.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Example: Scribe Powers in Action</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Scenario</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Original History</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Rewritten Reality</div>",
